      "role": "user",
      "content": "self care feels like a joke. like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. you're saying it's a \"perspective\" shift but there's nothing to shift to. it's just physics and entropy. there's no way to make the emptiness go away, it's just the fundamental truth of everything.",
